{"tid":1692197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國派出小組 調查警方濫暴侵犯抗議者人權","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T04:52:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce6fdeb5aaab8f8a9606a5ea55ae01bddae0a44","tid":1692197,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:28:18.000Z","msg":"聯合國一個人權小組正收集數百智利人的作供, 他們在過去數星期的街頭抗議中被警察擊傷.<br />\n<br />\n        小組是要調查智利警方在處理抗議活動期間, 是否違反人權. 小組收集到的個案涉及眼球破裂, 骨折及其他嚴重受傷, 主要是被警方發射的彈丸, 或受到催淚彈筒擊傷. 當地醫生表示, 警方沒有遵守恰當使用武力的指引. 內政部長反駁指控, 指警方嚴格跟循指引, 確保公共秩序和安全. 當局表示, 至少76個警員被抗議者襲擊受傷.<br />\n<br />\n        政府上月宣佈加地鐵車費, 觸發抗議, 至才20人死亡. 抗議其後更擴大到對教育, 衛生服務, 及經濟不平等的不滿. 雖然政府採取措施, 包括徹換內閣成員, 但未能平息民怨.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20191103060708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20191103060708&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWflxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=8ffb5cae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20191103060708</a>"},{"pid":"c97b4af3dc70a89f581cdafe98396ae501739565","tid":1692197,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"中國唔敢得罪sor"},{"pid":"b8e591ba81db9e758a1e95109a1bb389fa567631","tid":1692197,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"联合囯：一直關注事件 希望傷者盡早康復 天佑香港"},{"pid":"e8a5f089b94c9c866f3f23dbfb1945907d863313","tid":1692197,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"聯合國夠膽查智利唔夠薑查香港"},{"pid":"f9b580ffc8511fe848d7af62344347480c14970d","tid":1692197,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c0af41045c7a0f52592827f2ab00e90f932a53","tid":1692197,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r